description:
In https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/239854 we split milestones CSS out of application.css, which broke dark mode

1. Enable Dark mode (alpha)
1. Load milestones page
1. Background is white, text not viewable

Need to replace all SCSS variables with CSS custom properties, as defined in [_dark.scss](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/blob/8c58e99db001c64cc816b016130a1139011965c0/app/assets/stylesheets/themes/_dark.scss#L90)

Example:

```scss
// before
a {
  color: $gl-text-color;
}

// after
a {
  color: var(--gl-text-color, $gl-text-color);
}
```
